       S3500-QJL2754-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ QJL2754 OUTPUT
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3610-QJL2754-OUTPUT-RTN.

      *   출력라인수1 - 승인위원수
           MOVE DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
             TO XDJL0418-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

