           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ QJL4022 첨부파일 조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3600-QJL4022-CALL-RTN.

           INITIALIZE                  XQJL4022-IN

      *    그룹회사코드
           MOVE  BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  XQJL4022-I-GROUP-CO-CD
      *    한도신청번호
           MOVE  WK-LIMT-APLCN-NO
             TO  XQJL4022-I-LIMT-APLCN-NO

      *@3  프로그램 호출
           #DYSQLA  QJL4022  XQJL4022-CA

      *@3  호출결과 확인
           EVALUATE  TRUE
           WHEN  COND-DBSQL-OK
               PERFORM S3610-QJL4022-OUTPUT-RTN
                  THRU S3610-QJL4022-OUTPUT-EXT
           WHEN  COND-DBSQL-MRNF
      *         첨부파일여부
                 MOVE CO-CHA-0
                  TO XDJL0418-O-RPTDOC-APNDX

           WHEN  OTHER
               #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

           .
       S3600-QJL4022-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ QJL4022 OUTPUT
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3610-QJL4022-OUTPUT-RTN.

      *   출력라인수2 - 첨부파일수
           MOVE  DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
             TO  XDJL0418-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT2

      *   첨부파일여부
           IF    DBSQL-SELECT-CNT      > ZERO
                 MOVE CO-CHA-1
                  TO XDJL0418-O-RPTDOC-APNDX
           END-IF

           PERFORM VARYING  WK-K FROM   1  BY  1
                     UNTIL  WK-K >   DBSQL-SELECT-CNT

      *       첨부파일일련번호
               MOVE  XQJL4022-O-APNDX-FILE-SERNO(WK-K)
                 TO  XDJL0418-O-APNDX-FILE-SERNO(WK-K)

      *       첨부파일식별자
