               MOVE  XQJL4022-O-EMP-HANGL-FNAME(WK-K)
                 TO  XDJL0418-O-REGI-EMNM(WK-K)

      *       첨부파일내용
               MOVE  XQJL4022-O-APNDX-FILE-CTNT(WK-K)
                 TO  XDJL0418-O-APNDX-FILE-CTNT(WK-K)

